title: Element Make It Count - Spain 2015
description:
Congrats to POL CATENA who won the MAKE IT COUNT contest in Barcelona !
Pol won a spot in the European Finals that will take place in Italy and a chance to win a trip to California to compete for Element sponsorship at Nyjah's park!

More info : elementmakeitcount.com

Special thanks to https://elmonstrino.bandcamp.com for the music!

13 and Under:
1st – Luca Vers
2nd – Iker Puertas

14 to 16:
1st – Neyl Calle
2nd – Nacho Climent
3rd – Miquel Vidal

17+ and Sponsored:
1st – Pol Catena
2nd – Adrián García
3rd – David Castels
